    public class IntIntMap4a

implements IntIntMap
    An extremely fast int-int map for large data sets which avoids boxing costs. Original source from https://github.com/mikvor/hashmapTest. For performance information, see http://java-performance.info/implementing-world-fastest-java-int-to-int-hash-map/
